### ASP.NET Core 10 SSE Demo - HTTP Tests
### Test the Server-Sent Events endpoints directly

@host = http://localhost:5000

### Test SSE connection for user Alice
GET {{host}}/api/task-progress/alice
Accept: text/event-stream

### Test SSE connection with Last-Event-ID (reconnection simulation)
GET {{host}}/api/task-progress/bob
Accept: text/event-stream
Last-Event-ID: 2025-09-02T10:30:45.123Z

### Start a task for Alice
POST {{host}}/api/tasks/alice/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taskName": "Data Processing",
  "estimatedDuration": 15
}

### Start a task for Bob
POST {{host}}/api/tasks/bob/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taskName": "Report Generation", 
  "estimatedDuration": 10
}

### Get active users count
GET {{host}}/api/users/active

### Test with Charlie (concurrent user)
POST {{host}}/api/tasks/charlie/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taskName": "Database Backup",
  "estimatedDuration": 20
}

### SSE stream for Charlie
GET {{host}}/api/task-progress/charlie
Accept: text/event-stream
